<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#d03f3bc54e44e1cbc699f0c3dfac9af8>.
<#d03f3bc54e44e1cbc699f0c3dfac9af8> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://opendata.umea.se/api/v2/catalog/datasets/gop_lekparker>;
