    a <http://purl.org/dc/terms/PeriodOfTime>, <http://purl.org/dc/terms/Location>.
<https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/37f42bb3-86ca-4420-a71d-41a2d4ea7457> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#contactPoint> <https://www.smhi.se/data/utforskaren-oppna-data/oceanograf_smhi.se>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#distribution> <https://opendata-download-ocobs.smhi.se/api/inspire/ocobs-7.atom>, <https://opendata-view.smhi.se/oc-obs-wavedirectionmean/OF.PointObservation/wms?service=wms&request=getcapabilities>, <https://opendata.smhi.se/ocobs/api>, <https://www.smhi.se/data/hitta-data-for-en-plats/ladda-ner-observationer-fran-havet/waves>, <https://opendata-download-ocobs.smhi.se/api/version/latest/parameter/7.json>;
