<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#6c006c11d6efcbd86ba6d8cf9a1f8286>.
<#6c006c11d6efcbd86ba6d8cf9a1f8286> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/9c95eda0-89ec-11ea-a966-bfa48b38ccc2>;
