<https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/edb8b81b-dd7a-4a29-98ae-a454d2cfddcc> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/temporal> _:b0__584
}

<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#f841ad25bab28d36e61762fbe0e73577>.
<#f841ad25bab28d36e61762fbe0e73577> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
