<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#5867f66339defe2202e6f44d157b977d>.
<#5867f66339defe2202e6f44d157b977d> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://metadata.trafikverket.se/store/1/resource/977>;
