    a <http://purl.org/dc/terms/PeriodOfTime>.
<https://metadata.trafikverket.se/store/1/resource/688> <http://entryscape.org/terms/metadataIdentifier> "02aa68e4-bf95-4382-ac95-c1a2e21b9b5d";
