<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#3d3b25cc2f3fd3699bea5fc5c856e0a5>.
<#3d3b25cc2f3fd3699bea5fc5c856e0a5> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/cf5f830c-0216-43c0-af60-e8385dfef4e2>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#published> "2026-05-18T07:23:13.556Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>.
<#3d3b25cc2f3fd3699bea5fc5c856e0a5> {
<https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/cf5f830c-0216-43c0-af60-e8385dfef4e2> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#keyword> "Malmö stad", "skulptur";
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/accrualPeriodicity> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/frequency/WEEKLY>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/identifier> "cf5f830c-0216-43c0-af60-e8385dfef4e2";
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/accessRights> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/access-right/PUBLIC>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/language> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/language/SWE>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/publisher> <https://malmo.se/>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Denna datamängd innehåller data om offentlig konst placerad på allmän platsmark som ägs av Malmö stad.  \n\n__Attribut__  \n  \n+ `id` [identifierare för konstverket]  \n+ `source` [organisationsnr för förvaltande myndighet]  \n+ `title` [konstverkets titel]  \n+ `description` [beskrivning av konstverket]  \n+ `artform` [typ av konstverk]  \n+ `creator` [konstnärens namn]  \n+ `created` [år när konstverket skapades]  \n+ `artmedium` [material som användes för konstverket]  \n+ `artwork_surface` [stödjande material till konstverket]  \n+ `width` [konstverkets bredd]  \n+ `height` [konstverkets höjd]  \n+ `depth` [konstverkets djup]  \n+ `street` [gatuadress]  \n+ `city` [ort]  \n+ `region` [län]  \n+ `URL` [länk till ingångssida för mer information]  \n+ `image` [länkar till bilder på konstverket]  \n+ `rights` [namn på fotografen]  \n+ `license` [licensrättigheter för bilderna]  \n+ `timestamp` [objektets senaste uppdateringsdatum]  \n+ `geometry` [typ: Point, CRS: WGS84]  \n\nAttributen följer i stort [Specifikation för offentlig konst - version 1.0](https://lankadedata.se/spec/offentlig-konst/), framtagen av Nationell Dataverkstad. Specifikationens fält för longitud, latitud är här anpassade till GeoJSONs __geometry__-attribut.  "@sv, "This dataset contains data about public art placed on public land owned by the\nCity of Malmö.\n\n**Attribute**\n\n  * `id` [identifier for the artwork]\n  * `source` [organizational number of managing authority]\n  * `title` [title of the artwork]\n  * `description` [description of the artwork]\n  * `artform` [type of artwork]\n  * `creator` [artist's name]\n  * `created` [year when the artwork was created]\n  * `artmedium` [material used for the artwork]\n  * `artwork_surface` [supporting material for the artwork]\n  * `width` [width of the artwork]\n  * `height` [height of the artwork]\n  * `depth` [depth of the artwork]\n  * `street` [street address]\n  * `city` ​​[place]\n  * `region` [county]\n  * `URL` [link to home page for more information]\n  * `image` [links to images of the artwork]\n  * `rights` [name of photographer]\n  * `license` [license rights for the images]\n  * `timestamp` [the object's last update date]\n  * `geometry` [type: Point, CRS: WGS84]\n\nThe attributes largely follow [the Specification for Public Art - version\n1.0](https://lankadedata.se/spec/offentlig%2dkonst/) , developed by the\nNational Data Workshop. The specification's fields for longitude and latitude\nare here adapted to GeoJSON's **geometry** attribute.\n\n"@en, "Dette datasæt indeholder data om offentlig kunst placeret på offentlig jord\nejet af Malmø Kommune.\n\n**Attribut**\n\n  * `id` [identifikator for kunstværket]\n  * `source` [organisationsnummer for forvaltningsmyndighed]\n  * `title` [kunstværkets titel]\n  * `description` [beskrivelse af kunstværket]\n  * `artform` [kunsttype]\n  * `creator` [kunstnerens navn]\n  * `created` [år hvor kunstværket blev skabt]\n  * `artmedium` [materiale brugt til kunstværket]\n  * `artwork_surface` [støttemateriale til kunstværket]\n  * `width` [kunstværkets bredde]\n  * `height` [kunstværkets højde]\n  * `depth` [kunstværkets dybde]\n  * `street` [gadeadresse]\n  * `city` [sted]\n  * `region` [amt]\n  * `URL` [link til hjemmeside for mere information]\n  * `image` [links til billeder af kunstværket]\n  * `rights` [fotografens navn]\n  * `license` [licensrettigheder til billederne]\n  * `timestamp` [objektets seneste opdateringsdato]\n  * `geometry` [type: Punkt, CRS: WGS84]\n\nAttributterne følger i vid udstrækning [Specifikationen for Offentlig Kunst -\nversion 1.0](https://lankadedata.se/spec/offentlig%2dkonst/) , udviklet af\nNational Data Workshop. Specifikationens felter for længdegrad og breddegrad\ner her tilpasset GeoJSONs **geometriattribut** .\n\n"@da;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/spatial> <http://www.geonames.org/2692965/malmoe.html>, _:b0__3518.
_:b0__3518 <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#bbox> "POLYGON((12.8850967451 55.6421476735,13.1517619812 55.6421476735,13.1517619812 55.5022773196,12.8850967451 55.5022773196,12.8850967451 55.6421476735))"^^<http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#wktLiteral>;
    a <http://purl.org/dc/terms/Location>.
<https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/cf5f830c-0216-43c0-af60-e8385dfef4e2> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#contactPoint> <https://admin.dataportal.se/store/290/resource/abd7da407bcfbc956fd6c0e91189412f>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#distribution> <https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/cf5f830c-0216-43c0-af60-e8385dfef4e2/resource/01c13bc1-861c-4486-85a3-15d50ac6584e>, <https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/cf5f830c-0216-43c0-af60-e8385dfef4e2/resource/4d9d1717-5151-4662-a834-7caf840cec37>, <https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/cf5f830c-0216-43c0-af60-e8385dfef4e2/resource/fd1e5590-3a73-4fe7-9972-f7d6c9ab3fd6>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/issued> "2025-06-27"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/modified> "2026-05-16T08:29:32.107987"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "Offentlig konst"@sv, "Public art"@en, "Offentlig kunst"@da;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#theme> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme/EDUC>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/conformsTo> <https://lankadedata.se/spec/offentlig-konst/>;
    a <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#Dataset>
}

