<#a024403ca23cfcd5d5dd7c383b45ee10> {
<https://www.geodata.se/resources/22f4326a-afe1-410c-9325-8468bbe0f453> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/accrualPeriodicity> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/frequency/CONT>;
