<#daadf9d9234487a8963c896b3e2446d8> {
<https://www.geodata.se/resources/be2c7127-16ba-4fe9-a8df-5fc1b361e102> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/accrualPeriodicity> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/frequency/CONT>;
