<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#188aedb21db7236401e27b7695b0f42e>.
<#188aedb21db7236401e27b7695b0f42e> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://doi.org/10.5878/qkwj-2d05>;
