<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#0166c7a5c47cc52327a72a56e21147e0>.
<#0166c7a5c47cc52327a72a56e21147e0> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://doi.org/10.5878/002510>;
